articles.title: 2026 Indiana Fever Regular Season Schedule Announced - Indiana Fever
articles.description: Fever to open the season at home on May 9 against Dallas Wings  INDIANAPOLIS (Jan. 21, 2026) — The Indiana Fever has unveiled its complete, 44-game schedule for the 2026 WNBA season. Select tickets will go on sale at 2 p.m. ET on Thursday, Jan. 22. Fans can a…
